      "content": "\"Those outside agitators are just trying to stir the pot and mess up our good order,\" one might sneer, leaning in conspiratorially. \"We can't let some troublemakers come in here and tell us how to run our own town.\" Another might spit out a comment, \"They oughta stay where they belong, or we'll have to make sure they learn their place around here.\"",
